title: NASA's Perseverance Rover Shows Off Collection of Mars Samples
summary: The Red Planet rover snapped a portrait of the sample depot it has assembled with 10 backup sample tubes that could be returned to Earth by a future mission.

title: Elon Musk and astronaut Scott Kelly debate use of Starlink in Ukraine

title: NASA, Partners Clear Axiom’s Second Private Astronaut Mission Crew
summary: NASA and its international partners have approved the crew for Axiom Space’s second private astronaut mission to the International Space Station, Axiom Mission 2 (Ax-2).
